						 <p>This is the skip I'm going to point to when someone says &quot;What do you mean, tell a story.&quot;</p> <p>It's the little details that really cinch this up in my opinion. The realistic testing methodology (realistic-ish at least). Consistency with naming, and locations. This is really well done, Scanny.</p> <p>Easy +1</p> 
